WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.130 --> 00:00:11.150
to all my people

00:00:11.210 --> 00:00:13.220
East Africa

00:00:14.030 --> 00:00:18.060
in Tanzania, Uganda and Kenya

00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:22.130
in Dar es Salaam
in Arusha

00:00:22.190 --> 00:00:25.000
wherever you are

00:00:25.060 --> 00:00:28.060
kneel and pray to God

00:00:28.120 --> 00:00:33.090
what's the offence of the poor?
What is lawful and what is unlawful?

00:00:33.150 --> 00:00:36.190
is this politics, religion, slavery
judgement day, Sodom and Gomorrah?

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.090
stand strong
take a look around each corner

00:00:40.150 --> 00:00:43.060
left,right, front, back
make sure you look everywhere

00:00:43.120 --> 00:00:46.000
just listen and be patient
so that you won’t regret later on

00:00:46.060 --> 00:00:51.050
this goes out to my people
the cripple, blind, albinos or insane

00:00:51.110 --> 00:00:55.080
street children, beggars
and those who are mentally sane

00:00:55.140 --> 00:00:59.100
we're pulling the rope against those in power
fat bellies and cheeks

00:00:59.160 --> 00:01:02.200
it’s no longer a fair game
the referee is biased, the field is dry

00:01:03.010 --> 00:01:05.210
work is hard to find, payment is little
what’s left is to play the hard way

00:01:06.020 --> 00:01:10.240
tired of upper class, capitalism, dictatorship
this is the time of redemption

00:01:11.050 --> 00:01:14.140
I demand that the poor
should get that wine

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:19.240
I pour poison over your opponents
to make them scratch themselves without shame

00:01:20.050 --> 00:01:22.220
a salute to those who passed away before us
let us pray to God

00:01:23.030 --> 00:01:28.040
our father,give us our daily bread
fill us with strength to succeed

00:01:28.100 --> 00:01:32.050
on the day of judgement
give us the chance to regret

00:01:32.110 --> 00:01:35.160
because we know
we are eating forbidden fruits

00:01:35.220 --> 00:01:39.070
we use every possible method, juju, trickery
so we can sustain ourselves

00:01:39.130 --> 00:01:43.190
but that shouldn’t be a reason 
for others to rob our rights

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:48.020
to call us infidels and insult us

00:01:48.080 --> 00:01:50.050
what have we done wrong?

00:01:50.110 --> 00:01:54.200
what’s the offense of the poor?
what is wrong,what is right?

00:01:55.010 --> 00:02:00.190
everyone just wants their destiny
but you can’t look into the future

