00:02:11.170 --> 00:02:15.090
if we would all be intellectuals and rich

00:02:15.150 --> 00:02:22.070
who'd do the dirty and dangerous work
in the mortuary, sweeping the street, watchmen...

00:02:22.130 --> 00:02:27.220
everyone here in town came for a business
even a human skin is for sale

00:02:28.030 --> 00:02:32.180
some are fake healers and wizards
others gentle-mannered like Born-again Christians

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:36.010
in the afternoon offices are buzzing
while the night is hard, prostitutes,

00:02:36.070 --> 00:02:39.040
sugar daddies,criminals
and other things to be covered up

00:02:39.100 --> 00:02:43.170
those who died fighting for their lives
their memories remain in the graveyard

00:02:43.230 --> 00:02:48.020
those who lost hope that they will ever win
they have taken out a mortgage on their souls

